OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1777921886
OL,3,CCriminal investigation over 'hero'
OL,4,Cfisherman's death at sea
OL,6,FA criminal investigation has been
OL,7,Flaunched after a report found safety
OL,8,Ffailings contributed to the death of a
OL,9,Ffisherman as he tried to save his
OL,10,Fbrother in the North Sea.
OL,12,FJames Haughey, 24, and his younger
OL,13,Fbrother Josh were part of a crew of
OL,14,Ffive crab fishing off Grimsby in May
OL,15,F2024 when Josh was struck by a pot and
OL,16,Fknocked overboard.
OL,18,FJames, who was known as "Jimmy", went
OL,19,Finto the water to save his brother and
OL,20,FJosh was successfully hauled to safety.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1777921886
OL,3,CCriminal investigation over 'hero'
OL,4,Cfisherman's death at sea
OL,6,FBut James lost consciousness and
OL,7,Fdrowned. His body was later recovered
OL,8,Fby a second vessel.
OL,10,FA spokesperson for the government's
OL,11,FMaritime and Coastguard Agency (MCA)
OL,12,Fsaid a criminal inquiry was now
OL,13,Funderway.
OL,15,FThey said: "The circumstances are
OL,16,Fsubject to criminal investigation by
OL,17,Fthe MCA's Regulatory Compliance
OL,18,FInvestigations Team.
OL,26,@wD@LOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1777921886
OL,3,CCriminal investigation over 'hero'
OL,4,Cfisherman's death at sea
OL,6,F"Our thoughts remain with the loved
OL,7,Fones of the deckhand who tragically
OL,8,Flost his life."
OL,10,FIt comes as a report by the Marine
OL,11,FAccident Investigation Branch (MAIB)
OL,12,Fidentified a series of safety issues
OL,13,Fon the boat, called Weston Bay.
OL,15,FJames' partner, Molly Marsden,
OL,16,Fdescribed him as a hero and said that
OL,17,Fhe had been failed.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@OO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1777921886
OL,3,CCriminal investigation over 'hero'
OL,4,Cfisherman's death at sea
OL,6,F"He saved his brother didn't he?
OL,7,FThat's just the epitome of James," she
OL,8,Fsaid. "That just sums him up in one
OL,9,Fact. Even if it wasn't his brother
OL,10,Fhe'd have done it for anybody.
OL,12,F"It shouldn't have happened. He
OL,13,Fshould've come home. No one should go
OL,14,Fto work and not come home. It's
OL,15,Fdevastating.
OL,17,F"It's been the hardest two years of my
OL,18,Flife."
OL,20,FWhat the report found
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1777921886
OL,3,CCriminal investigation over 'hero'
OL,4,Cfisherman's death at sea
OL,6,FThe MAIB found multiple issues
OL,7,F"directly contributing to the
OL,8,Faccident" on the boat, which was owned
OL,9,Fby Fastline Shellfish Ltd, along with
OL,10,Fother problems which needed to be
OL,11,Faddressed.
OL,13,FIt said the emergency ladder was in
OL,14,F"very poor condition" and
OL,15,F"catastrophically failed and fell
OL,16,Fapart" when James attempted to use it.
OL,18,FThe boat lacked effective safe systems
OL,19,Fof work to prevent the crew being too
OL,20,Fclose to fishing equipment, and this
OL,21,Fled to Josh being taken into the sea.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1777921886
OL,3,CCriminal investigation over 'hero'
OL,4,Cfisherman's death at sea
OL,6,FThe report said the crew had not
OL,7,Froutinely conducted emergency drills,
OL,8,Fwith the most recent being recorded
OL,9,Fsix months before the accident.
OL,11,FThe risks associated with an
OL,12,Finexperienced crew had not been
OL,13,Fconsidered, which meant Josh was faced
OL,14,Fwith an unfamiliar task in a hazardous
OL,15,Fposition in front of the pot stack,
OL,16,Fplacing him at risk of injury and harm.
OL,18,FThe investigation also found there
OL,19,Fwere no instructions for using
OL,20,Fflotation devices and crew had not
OL,21,Fbeen instructed on their use.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1777921886
OL,3,CCriminal investigation over 'hero'
OL,4,Cfisherman's death at sea
OL,6,FMAIB inspector, Antony Shine, said the
OL,7,FWeston Bay "didn't have effective safe
OL,8,Fsystems of work".
OL,10,F"Once they were in the sea, (the crew)
OL,11,Fhadn't carried out emergency drills -
OL,12,Fthe emergency preparedness on the
OL,13,Fvessel (wasn't there).
OL,15,F"They didn't have the muscle memory to
OL,16,Freact in that instance, so although
OL,17,Fthey did the best they could with the
OL,18,Flimited equipment they had, they were
OL,19,Funable to recover the second deckhand."
OL,26,@rD@]pmrD@fpnuD@HpmuD@Upn
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1777921886
OL,3,CCriminal investigation over 'hero'
OL,4,Cfisherman's death at sea
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV Calendar about the
OL,7,Fmoment she found out about the
OL,8,Fincident, Molly said: "I was at work
OL,9,Fand I was on my dinner break talking
OL,10,Fto my friends.
OL,12,F"I was actually talking about James,
OL,13,Fand then I got a message from his
OL,14,Fsister on my phone saying that James
OL,15,Fhad been in an accident. I said,
OL,16,F'what's he gone and done now, has he
OL,17,Fbroke his leg, has he hurt his arm?'
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1777921886
OL,3,CCriminal investigation over 'hero'
OL,4,Cfisherman's death at sea
OL,6,F"Then we got a phone call from someone
OL,7,Fthat works down the dock and they said
OL,8,F'he's gone'. I just stood up and I
OL,9,Fwent into the kitchen, and screamed."
OL,11,FShe added: "I feel a bit stuck,
OL,12,Fbecause we're so young and you plan
OL,13,Feverything together don't you. And now
OL,14,FI feel like for the rest of my life
OL,15,FI'm going to be comparing everything
OL,16,Fto him."
OL,26,@qD@eO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G9/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1777921886
OL,3,CCriminal investigation over 'hero'
OL,4,Cfisherman's death at sea
OL,6,FKallum Kirk, James' former crewmate
OL,7,Fand friend, said: "It makes me feel
OL,8,Fsick is what it makes me feel, because
OL,9,Fthat could've been me or could've been
OL,10,Fany number of any other friends who
OL,11,FI've met in fishing that have got
OL,12,Ffamilies to go home to.
OL,14,F"Jimmy was like a brother to me, it's
OL,15,Flike I've lost a brother and that day
OL,16,Fit's like I nearly lost two brothers.
OL,26,@oD@SOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G10/12
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1777921886
OL,3,CCriminal investigation over 'hero'
OL,4,Cfisherman's death at sea
OL,6,F"It's a dangerous job and everybody
OL,7,Fthat gets involved with it knows it's
OL,8,Fa dangerous job. And you go on boats
OL,9,Fand they all know what they're doing,
OL,10,Fit's all strict, to the book and to
OL,11,Fthe letter. Because if it's not,
OL,12,Fpeople lose lives, people get injured,
OL,13,Fpeople don't come home."
OL,15,FFastline Shellfish Ltd declined to
OL,16,Fcomment while investigations were
OL,17,Fbeing carried out.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1        G11/12
